<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        text-decoration: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added toyour question in the video "<%= title %>"</p>
    <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
    <p>Thanks you for being a part of our community</p>
</body>
</html>